skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: basketball doctor
des:
List injured player(s) and injuries for given team. Team names can be given as full name like "Portland Trail Blazers" or just short name "Blazers"

User will ask for injury list and players for a team and Alexa will reply with the injured players and their ailment.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
